::Prowl/Kluster::

Kluster smiles at Iron Raptor, his eyes going over her as he shakes her hand. 
She wasn't too bad, not a bad looking femm at all....

He smiles at her, "I'm glad you aproove of the ship, Commander," he says, 
stepping aside to let Iron Raptor talk with Battera.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl frowns, his eyes narrowing as he sees Kluster admire Iron Raptor. A 
wave of jealousy washes over him, followed by fear. What if Iron Raptor was 
mad enough at his insult to leave him for Kluster? He could lose her!

He walks toward, her, trying to put his arm around her again. His optics take 
on a looks of hostility toward Kluster, but the commander of the Cybertronian 
Fire wasn't looking at him.
